Select * From [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_523_SRVCARD] [LS]


Select NAME From [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_623_ITEMS]
Select NAME From [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_723_ITEMS]
Select NAME From [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_623_CLCARD]
Select * From [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_523_CLCARD] Where DEFINITION_ Like '%Ä°SKUR%'

Select NAME From [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LKSDB].[dbo].[L_CAPIWHOUSE]

Select * From [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_623_01_STFICHE] F
Inner Join  [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_623_01_STLINE] FL On F.LOGICALREF = FL.STFICHEREF



Select F.FICHENO, CL.DEFINITION_, I.CODE, I.NAME, FL.AMOUNT From [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_723_01_STFICHE] F
Inner Join  [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_723_01_STLINE] FL On F.LOGICALREF = FL.STFICHEREF
Inner Join  [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_723_CLCARD] CL On F.CLIENTREF = CL.LOGICALREF
Inner Join  [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_723_ITEMS] I On I.LOGICALREF = FL.STOCKREF
Where I.NAME Like '%63%' And CL.DEFINITION_ Like '%DANI%'
Order By F.LOGICALREF Desc



Select F.FICHENO, CL.DEFINITION_, I.CODE, I.NAME, FL.AMOUNT From [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_623_01_STFICHE] F
Inner Join  [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_623_01_STLINE] FL ON F.LOGICALREF = FL.STFICHEREF
INNER JOIN  [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_623_CLCARD] CL ON F.CLIENTREF = CL.LOGICALREF
INNER JOIN  [LOGOENTEGRASYON].[LOGOTIGER].[dbo].[LG_623_ITEMS] I ON I.LOGICALREF = FL.STOCKREF
WHERE I.NAME like '%63%'  AND F.TRCODE = 8
ORDER BY F.LOGICALREF desc
